Templates are HTML files with special DTL tags for dynamic content.

DTL Syntax:
- {{ variable }} — output a value
- {% tag %} — logic tags
- {# comment #} — template comments
- {{ value|filter }} — apply a filter

Common Tags:
- {% if %} {% elif %} {% else %} {% endif %}
- {% for item in list %} {% endfor %}
- {% block name %} {% endblock %}
- {% extends 'base.html' %}
- {% include 'partial.html' %}
- {% url 'name' %}
- {% static 'path' %}
- {% csrf_token %}

